      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements at 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error 38%; systematic over-prediction observed at high rotational speeds. Validation activity conducted on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under controlled laboratory conditions."
