      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares geometric family with the VAD device but is not the same geometry. Blood analog (glycerol-water) differs from patient blood rheology. Operating envelope coverage is partial. Achieved level 2 is substantially below the MRL-5 requirement of level 5."
