      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation setup review process with independent verification of boundary conditions, material properties, and solver settings by a qualified second analyst.",
      "rationale": "No independent review of simulation setup was conducted. A single analyst configured and executed all simulations. Use-error risk is unmitigated at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 versus required level 4."
