      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification that the chosen turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model are appropriate for the flow regimes present in the VAD; comparison of at least two turbulence models documented.",
      "rationale": "The k-omega SST turbulence model was used without comparison to alternative turbulence closures. Model form uncertainty for the hemolysis power-law constitutive relation was not quantified. This is a critical epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 versus required level 5."
